{"id":773192,"date":[{"year":1988,"month":6,"day":24}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"374","ytitle":"","mtitle":"梧桐树(外一首)","ftitle":"","authors":["郭在精"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭在精"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你垂吊一个个小黑球，象音符；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你舒展嫩黄的枝叶，象彩笔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会说话么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉默不语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋天来了，锈蚀了你的面容；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天来了，折损了你的身躯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这里多凄凉，没有一丝春意!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几只小鸟飞来又飞去，喳喳叽叽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你会说话么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉默不语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪纷飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你披上了洁白的外衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风呼呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你荡漾起一个个跳跃的音符。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，这跳跃的音符"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是你心底的话语?……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个人都有你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个你各相异"}]}